digitalx_direct.py is a simple python wrapper for interacting with the DigitalX Direct ReST API for ordering bitcoins and retrieving BTC quote information. It requires a DigitalX Direct account, you can request a test account by emailing neel@digitalbtc.com. 

Please direct any questions about the code or the DigitalX Direct Bitcoin Liquidity Platform
to neel@digitalbtc.com as well. 